# Roadmap

This file is the top-level entry point to the project roadmap. Each phase
is a separate file in `roadmaps/phases/`, each initiative in
`roadmaps/initiatives/`, and each milestone in `roadmaps/milestones/`.

The index at `roadmaps/_index.md` (auto-generated) provides a summary
table of all items. Edit the individual files to update statuses, then
run `pctl reindex` to refresh the index.

